{"tid":1720650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當面狠批中国有多壞   川普：習當時一定很生氣","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:12:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b1f70cec10ad60420cf9dfe6432efdc097cf8d","tid":1720650,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普屢稱與中國國家主席習近平交情良好，但他近日在公開場合自爆，過去訪中時曾當著包含習在內的5000多人面前，大肆批評中國有多壞，認為「習當時一定很生氣」，但他最後將矛頭指向自家人，批評是前任總統們對中國的作為視若無睹，才會使美國的利益受損。<br />\n<br />\n川普週二在紐約經濟俱樂部演說，提及上任3年來的經濟成就並數落中國的不是，導致許多美國工廠關閉；川普提到，先前在中國發表演說時，當著習近平及5000多人的面批評中國有多麼地壞；川普描述當時的心境，認為「這下糟了，我人在北京，看著台下的習近平臉色莊重，想必他一定很生氣。」<br />\n<br />\n川普接著說，「要怎麼挽救這個局勢呢？下午的行程一定會是一場災難」，因此他話鋒一轉，高呼「我不怪中國，我責怪的是我們的領導人」，認為中國的所作所為都是美國前任總統們的放任、不作為，才導致今日的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/11/14/phpknxASH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F11%2F14%2FphpknxASH.jpg&h=2d6fb2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2977434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2977434&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVcwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a977123a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2977434&h=360f1bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2977434</a>"},{"pid":"236b3f1824a06cc01a8d12ff7f780a34ce55c5eb","tid":1720650,"uid":74696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387b5b2962db469add74ae0c5a5e1279b6f255ef","tid":1720650,"uid":21002,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"撚識英文咩"},{"pid":"051ef3a